OL,6,FA carer who stole more than #20,000
OL,7,Ffrom a disabled woman she was caring
OL,8,Ffor, left her with no heating while
OL,9,Fspending thousands on clothes.
OL,11,FPetula Hatzer, 55, was employed by
OL,12,FAlison Doyle's family for 17 years to
OL,13,Flook after Alison who has cerebral
OL,14,Fpalsy, epilepsy and dystonia. She is
OL,15,Fnon-verbal and requires 24-hour live-
OL,16,Fin carers.
