OL,6,FHatzer was seen as a family friend and
OL,7,Feven went to the funeral of Alison's
OL,8,Ffather. She was trusted to be in a
OL,9,Fmanagerial position and manage her
OL,10,Ffinances. She was even given a bank
OL,11,Fcard under the name of Lilian Doyle,
OL,12,FAlison's mother's name.
OL,14,FThe offences were investigated when
OL,15,Fother carers for Ms Doyle became
OL,16,Fconcerned about deliveries that were
OL,17,Fclearly not for her, Manchester's
OL,18,FMinshull Street Crown Court heard.
