OL,6,FThe police discovered Hatzer had been
OL,7,Fspending her money on clothes and
OL,8,Fitems from websites including Next,
OL,9,FAmazon and Very.
OL,11,FProsecutors believe she stole an
OL,12,Festimated #20,000, creating credit
OL,13,Faccounts to nine different stores,
OL,14,Fincluding Curvissa and Freemans.
OL,16,FHatzer, of, , pleaded guilty to 10
OL,17,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,18,Frepresentation; and one count of fraud
OL,19,Fby abuse of position. She has been
OL,20,Fjailed for under a year and two months.
