OL,6,F"The defendant admitted making nine
OL,7,Fdifferent accounts under the name of
OL,8,FAlison Doyle for a number of
OL,9,Forganisations, including Next, to the
OL,10,Famount of #4,500.
OL,12,F"She also pleaded guilty to a similar
OL,13,Foffence in respect of the Very group,
OL,14,Fto the amount of #2,500.
OL,16,F"During this time the defendant was in
OL,17,Fcontrol of the funds and on many
OL,18,Foccasions would ask Lilian Doyle for
OL,19,Fmore money due to insufficient funds,"
OL,20,Fthe prosecutor added.
