OL,6,FHatzer withdrew money from cash
OL,7,Fmachines, putting it into her own bank
OL,8,Faccount. She had made many payments to
OL,9,FAmazon for items which were not for Ms
OL,10,FDoyle.JSharron Clark, Ms Doyle's
OL,11,Fsister, read a victim impact statement
OL,12,Fin court. She said: "We have all been
OL,13,Fdeeply affected by what has happened,
OL,14,Fbut especially my mum and Alison.
OL,16,F"My mum had seen Petula as her best
OL,17,Ffriend and trusted her with her life,
OL,18,Fbut because of what she has done, my
OL,19,Fmum is too frightened to even be
OL,20,Fanywhere near her.
