OL,6,F"Petula, known as Pet to us, became
OL,7,Fthe manager of the team, and her long
OL,8,Fservice became an important part of
OL,9,FAlison's life.
OL,11,F"Pet was held in high regard so much
OL,12,Fthat our mother regarded her as
OL,13,Fanother daughter, and the rest of us
OL,14,Fas a member of the family. Alison also
OL,15,Fadored her.
