OL,6,F"For a long time before Pet became
OL,7,Fmanager, my mum and I took charge of a
OL,8,Flot of things but as my mum aged and I
OL,9,Fbecame unwell, having to have heart
OL,10,Fsurgery, we both took a step back and
OL,11,Ffelt comfortable with Pet taking
OL,12,Fcontrol of things.
OL,14,F"Unbeknown to us she would use her new
OL,15,Fmanagerial position to financially
OL,16,Fabuse such a vulnerable person and
OL,17,Ftake advantage of our trust for her.
OL,18,FHer actions have destroyed our faith
OL,19,Fin humanity.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
