OL,6,F"We still cannot understand how she
OL,7,Fcould use a vulnerable person, such as
OL,8,Four Alison, to make a financial gain
OL,9,Ffrom her and a family that loved her
OL,10,Funconditionally.
OL,12,F"She even attended our father's
OL,13,Ffuneral, he knew and trusted Pet and
OL,14,Fwould be so shocked if he was alive,
OL,15,Fhaving fought so hard to get Alison
OL,16,Fher independence with the security to
OL,17,Flive her life with trusted people
OL,18,Fclose to her.
