OL,6,F"The person we trusted most
OL,7,Fmanipulated and lied to us. Alison's
OL,8,Fhome, equipment and clothes were not
OL,9,Fto the standard we expected.
OL,11,F"The heating was not used, and Alison
OL,12,Fand the carers had to wear additional
OL,13,Fclothes and cover Alison with blankets
OL,14,Fto keep her warm. This is on the basis
OL,15,Fthat Pet told them the heating was not
OL,16,Fincluded in the budget.
OL,18,F"As a family we have been left
OL,19,Fseverely traumatised by what has
OL,20,Fhappened."
