OL,6,FNeil Ronan, defending Hatzer, who has
OL,7,Fno previous convictions, said was in a
OL,8,Fcontrolling relationship and racked up
OL,9,Fdebt which led to her declaring
OL,10,Fpartial bankruptcy.
OL,12,FMr Ronan told the court his client's
OL,13,Fgrandchild, born with genetic
OL,14,Fabnormalities, has been given only a
OL,15,Fyear to live.
OL,17,FHe said: "She is distressed and
OL,18,Fabsolutely beside herself at what she
OL,19,Fhas done. She has lived beyond her
OL,20,Fmeans. She acknowledges the harm and
OL,21,Funderstands the harm she has caused.
