OL,6,F"If she is sent to prison, there is a
OL,7,Fhigh likelihood he will not make it to
OL,8,Fthe end of her sentence."
OL,10,FJailing her, Recorder Michael
OL,11,FArmstrong said: "This has had a
OL,12,Fprofound and long lasting effect on
OL,13,Fthe family who only wanted the best
OL,14,Ffor their daughter and their sister.
OL,16,F"These offences do have tragic
OL,17,Fconsequences causing grief to two
OL,18,Ffamilies. This was a horrendous breach
OL,19,Fof trust.
